</div></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">授業計画</div><div style="margin:10px"><p>This course will introduce film studies while helping you to improve your English. </p>
<p>The schedule below shows the content for each week's lesson. </p>
<ol>
<li>Early Cinema</li>
<li>The Birth of Hollywood</li>
<li>1920s Russian and German Cinema</li>
<li>Synchronized Sound</li>
<li>Musicals</li>
<li>Animation</li>
<li>WWII Propoganda Films</li>
<li>Post-War Cinema</li>
<li>Film Noir</li>
<li>The Hollywood 10</li>
<li>Censorship and Certification</li>
<li>Exploitation Films</li>
<li>Blockbusters</li>
<li>Home Cinema</li>
<li>The Evolution of CGI</li>
<li>Comic Book Films</li>
</ol>
